---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Irene Wang — Ongoing Practice"
  description="Design, AI, smart environments, and ongoing curiosities. "
>
  <div class="home">
    <section class="home-hero">
      <div class="home-hero-copy">
        <p class="home-kicker">PERSONAL WEBSITE / WORK / EXPERIMENTS / RESEARCH</p>

        <h1 class="home-title">
          <span>Irene Wang</span>
        </h1>
        <h1 class="home-title">
          <span>— Ongoing Practice</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="home-lead">
         <span class="home-lead-en">
            Design, AI, smart environments, and ongoing curiosities.
          </span>
        
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

  <section class="home-entry-grid card-grid" aria-label="Main content paths">
      <a class="entry-card" href="/design">
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h3 class="entry-card-title">设计作品</h3>
          <p class="entry-card-desc">Spatial, visual, interface, and concept-driven design work.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>

      <a class="entry-card" href="/projects">
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h3 class="entry-card-title">实践项目</h3>
          <p class="entry-card-desc">Experiments, prototypes, making processes, and built outcomes.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>

      <a class="entry-card" href="/ai">
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h3 class="entry-card-title">AI 尝试</h3>
          <p class="entry-card-desc">Tools, workflows, prompting, prototypes, and applied AI thinking.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>

      <a class="entry-card" href="/research">
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h3 class="entry-card-title">学术研究</h3>
          <p class="entry-card-desc">Questions, papers, references, and evolving research interests.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="home-about" aria-labelledby="home-about-title">
      <div class="home-about-copy">
        <h2 id="home-about-title" class="about-title">About me</h2>
        <div class="about-pairs">
          <div class="about-pair">
            <p class="cn">我关心设计、技术、AI 与智能环境交汇的地方，也持续观察空间、系统与人的关系如何被重新组织。</p>
            <p class="en">I am fascinated by the intersection of design, technology, AI and intelligent environments, and I keep observing how the relationships among space, systems and people are being restructured.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-pair">
            <p class="cn">作品、实验、研究与书写，对我来说是同一件事的不同切面。</p>
            <p class="en">Works, experiments, research and writing are different facets of one and the same thing to me.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-pair">
            <p class="cn">这里既展示结果，也保留过程——一些仍在生长中的方法、判断与感受。</p>
            <p class="en">It presents both outcomes and preserves the process — methodologies, judgments, and sensibilities still in the making.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="home-about-side">
        <div class="home-about-card">
          <p class="home-about-label">Focus：Design / AI / Smart Environments / Research</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="home-about-actions">
          <a class="home-inline-link" href="/resume">查看简历</a>
        </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <script type="module" src="/src/scripts/aria-audit.js"></script>
</BaseLayout>
